  "title": "Mob Vision",
  "description": "Mob Vision Glowing mobs near player",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support%20me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Patreon\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join%20our%20Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\"></a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support%20me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a></p>\n<h2 data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"82\"><strong>Mob Vision</strong></h2>\n<p>Easily spot mobs around you, even through walls.<br data-start=\"132\" data-end=\"135\">This pack highlights all nearby mobs within a 25-block radius.</p>\n<h3 data-start=\"246\" data-end=\"259\">Features:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"318\">Applies the glowing effect to all nearby non-player mobs</li>\n<li data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"372\">Works whether holding an item or with an empty hand</li>\n<li data-start=\"375\" data-end=\"409\">Updates automatically in real time</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"450\" data-end=\"468\">Compatibility:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"508\">Minecraft Java Edition 1.17 and above</li>\n<li data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"553\">Works in both singleplayer and multiplayer</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1233/295/image_2025-06-27_225345377-png.png\" width=\"693\" height=\"430\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1233/294/image_2025-06-27_225336227-png.png\" width=\"691\" height=\"400\"></p>",
